OL,3,CGAA official murder public inquiry
OL,4,Cappeal to be fast tracked
OL,6,FAn appeal against the Northern Ireland
OL,7,FSecretary being ordered to set up a
OL,8,Fpublic inquiry into the murder of GAA
OL,9,Fofficial Sean Brown has been fast-
OL,10,Ftracked for a hearing next week.
OL,12,FThe UK Government is challenging the
OL,13,Fjudicial direction issued last month
OL,14,Fafter it was found to remain in breach
OL,15,Fof a human rights duty to probe the
OL,16,Ffull extent of state collusion in the
OL,17,FMay 1997 killing.
OL,19,FThe UK Government lodged an appeal on
OL,20,FNew Year's Eve.
