OL,6,FLady Chief Justice Dame Siobhan Keegan
OL,7,Fconfirmed that the Court of Appeal
OL,8,Fwill hear the case on January 16.
OL,10,FShe said: "This case has been before
OL,11,Fthe courts now for a long period of
OL,12,Ftime. I will provide expedition."
OL,14,FMr Brown, 61, was abducted by a
OL,15,FLoyalist Volunteer Force gang as he
OL,16,Flocked the gates at Bellaghy Wolfe
OL,17,FTones GAA Club in Co Derry.
OL,19,FThe father of six was bundled into the
OL,20,Fboot of his car, taken to Randalstown,
OL,21,FCo Antrim and shot dead.
