OL,6,FNo-one has ever been convicted of his
OL,7,Fmurder.
OL,9,FIt emerged last year at an inquest
OL,10,Fthat state agents were among more than
OL,11,F25 people linked by intelligence to
OL,12,Fthe killing.
OL,14,FAt that stage the coroner halted
OL,15,Fproceedings due to the extent of
OL,16,Fconfidential material excluded or
OL,17,Fwithheld on national security grounds.
OL,19,FHe wrote to the previous Conservative
OL,20,FGovernment requesting the
OL,21,Festablishment of a public inquiry.
