OL,6,FThe Court of Appeal has already ruled
OL,7,Fthat parts of the legislation breaches
OL,8,Fhuman rights law, with the Government
OL,9,Fhaving too much power to prohibit the
OL,10,FCommission from sharing sensitive
OL,11,Finformation.
OL,13,FMr Brown's 87-year-old widow, Bridie,
OL,14,Fmounted a successful High Court
OL,15,Fchallenge against the decision not to
OL,16,Fset up a public inquiry into her
OL,17,Fhusband's death.
