OL,6,FIn December, Mr Justice Humpreys
OL,7,Fcompelled the Secretary of State to
OL,8,Ftake the step after identifying a
OL,9,F"clear and unambiguous obligation" to
OL,10,Festablish such a statutory probe.
OL,12,FHe held there was no viable
OL,13,Falternative to a public inquiry
OL,14,Frequired to satisfy the state's
OL,15,Finvestigative duty under Article 2 of
OL,16,Fthe European Convention on Human
OL,17,FRights.
